[Though livestock anthrax is rife in Guinea with significant numbers of outbreaks and livestock losses, there are no prior OIE reports of it in this prefecture, which might explain the diagnostic problems.

Koubia in northern Guinea can be found on the map at http://www.lib.utexas.edu/maps/africa/guinea_pol02.jpg. - Mod.MHJ

A HealthMap/ProMED-mail map can be accessed at: https://promedmail.org/promed-post?place=2504182,39325.]
